{"tid":1576853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【嚴正警告　求幫推】　前線唔好再寫遺書擺係自己書包！！！","createTime":"2019-09-17T12:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T23:26:50.000Z","uid":14328,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d866f6dfaeb0f81a625f818158098f21c3403d56","tid":1576853,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"警察拘捕左你，如果搜到你封遺書<br />\n用最壞既動機去諗中國人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你可能會有生命危險</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係想嚇大家<br />\n而家咁多浮屍案、無聲跳樓，差唔多單單都搵到遺書。<br />\n<br />\n最近仲要有個女人，「自殺」之後，<br />\n條屍短短幾日溶到得返骨，掉左落海<br />\n完全唔敢想像佢死之前經歷左啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n香港人而家應該要做既，<br />\n係搞一個不自殺宣言<br />\n喺Twitter / Facebook 用英文講明<br />\n<br />\nI would not suicide. If I did, it is done by China Communist Party<br />\n<br />\n我最怕見到既係，警察如果搜到你封遺書，就將你送去新屋嶺&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"49274db2de51ce2ba3b871f0b49e5656af2d3b4f","tid":1576853,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"【極重要】（被？）自殺的失蹤人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc23e3d53891548c80b30c201c8f5316cfa4730f","tid":1576853,"uid":266172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"我相信封遺書無人會話係自殺吧"},{"pid":"4ca998dbe97d027fe6cd36eb271d575d9a3681b7","tid":1576853,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"Ff玩膠撚收皮啦好嗎"},{"pid":"504d1497a026c90300573153ea1333c5b1761a04","tid":1576853,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca998dbe97d027fe6cd36eb271d575d9a3681b7","tid":1576853,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"Ff玩膠撚收皮啦好嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"mug 9"},{"pid":"6f4a10f67d38e87ca372dcd89e769bca4d3eafe1","tid":1576853,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike"